# Local Workers dev vars — copy to .dev.vars and fill in real values.
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored; this file is the template that lives in source.
#
# These power the /api/spotify/now-playing route used by the NowPlaying
# component. Generate them once against your own Spotify account and reuse:
#
#   1. Create an app at https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
#   2. Use the authorization-code flow with scope `user-read-currently-playing`
#      to obtain the refresh token (one-time exchange).
#
# In production these go into the Cloudflare dashboard as Secrets (not Vars) —
# see DEPLOYMENT.md.

SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=
SPOTIFY_REFRESH_TOKEN=
